' Notes
note right of UC1
  Creates a new application record
  linked to a job listing.
  Sets initial target submission date.
end note

note bottom of UC2
  Records submission details including
  method, confirmation number, and
  submitted documents.
end note

note right of UC3
  Updates application to next stage
  in the hiring process. Maintains
  complete status history.
end note

note bottom of UC20
  Kanban-style board view allowing
  drag-and-drop status updates.
  Visual pipeline of all applications.
end note

